# Always Use Bun Package Manager Rules

## Package Management
- Always use `bun` or `bunx` for installing packages instead of npm/yarn/pnpm
- Use `bun add <package>` for dependencies
- Use `bun add -d <package>` for dev dependencies
- Use `bunx <command>` for running package executables (e.g., `bunx create-next-app`)
